Class AbstractLocalFileIngestDriver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.ingest.AbstractLocalFileDriver<LocalFileIngestPlugin<?>,LocalIngestRunData>
      • org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.ingest.AbstractLocalFileIngestDriver
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BaseDataStoreIngestDriver, LocalFileIngestCLIDriver

    public abstract class AbstractLocalFileIngestDriver
extends AbstractLocalFileDriver<LocalFileIngestPlugin<?>,LocalIngestRunData>
    This extends the local file driver to directly ingest data into GeoWave utilizing the LocalFileIngestPlugin's that are discovered by the system.
